---
title: Mushroom & Chicken Udon Noodle Stir-Fry with Asian Greens & Crispy Shallots
description: Load your bowl with tender udon noodles plus a medley of colourful veggies and tasty chicken. With our Asian stir-fry sauce
to bring the whole meal together, this feast will have you throwing away the takeaway menu!
